chleb-bible-search (2.5.0) stable; urgency=high

  * 🍪 add preferred translation settings and remember translation/search preferences
  * 🚸 it is now possible to set your preferred translation(s) and compare verses in one view
  * ✨ add JWT token repository support for session handling
  * 🔧 enable JWT-backed sessions for development and Debian deployments
  * ✨ add stateless search pagination and remember search page size
  * 💄 improve translated lookup rendering, search results, info tables, and verse navigation
  * ✨ add HTML modes for ping, version, uptime, and related route presentation
  * 🐛 support `application/vnd.api+json` while preserving `application/json`
  * 📦 move vendored Perl dependencies into the core package
  * 🔧 switch logging to stream/journal output and remove logrotate dependency
  * 🚸 improve systemd, SysV init, and local dev-server support
  * 🧪 expand functional HTTP coverage across settings, cookies, lookup, search, random, VOTD, and sessions
  * 💚 update CI, Dependabot, and pre-commit wiring for the new workflow

